      "text": "Mr. Green. Frakking?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 9170.0,
      "end_time": 11460.0,
      "text": "You don’t know about Battlestar Galactica yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 11460.0,
