      "text": "Me From The Past?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 12080.0,
      "end_time": 12620.0,
      "text": "Oh, man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 12620.0,
      "end_time": 13610.0,
      "text": "there are so many great"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 13610.0,
      "end_time": 14809.0,
      "text": "things in your future. [like Regretsy.com &amp; My Drunk Kitchen]"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 14809.0,
      "end_time": 17850.0,
      "text": "Today, I’m going to try to show you how tiny Spain’s influence spread around the"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 17850.0,
      "end_time": 21490.0,
      "text": "world and shaped the lives of almost every human on the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 21490.0,
      "end_time": 22890.0,
      "text": "generally in negative ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 22890.0,
      "end_time": 23500.0,
      "text": "I know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 23500.0,
      "end_time": 25119.0,
      "text": "everything is such a bummer on Crash Course recently."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 25119.0,
      "end_time": 25369.0,
      "text": "[Holy Atlantic Slave Trade, Batman]"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 25369.0,
      "end_time": 26590.0,
      "text": "It’s the sixteenth century."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 26590.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "People are getting richer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 31289.0,
      "text": "they’re living more connected lives and all I can do is whine about how much better"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 31289.0,
      "end_time": 32689.0,
      "text": "the old days were."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 32689.0,
      "end_time": 33960.0,
      "text": "What am I, your grandpa?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 33960.0,
      "end_time": 35949.0,
